{"tid":2179813,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"分享一個減食方法","createTime":"2020-08-29T11:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T05:54:36.000Z","uid":71166,"like":19,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"735b136a90c83de2045ed43819eef44fd98f8495","tid":2179813,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:39:48.000Z","msg":"大家會唔會好多時突然好想食一樣嘢<br />\n我會突然好想食炒飯，炸雞，打邊爐，肥肉（零食汽水吸引唔到我）<br />\n減緊肥又唔食得<br />\n我搵到個有效控制食慾嘅方法<br />\n就係用後置鏡頭影下自己個樣<br />\n就知自己幾肥成個山東婆咁，好樣衰，塊面黃咁咁，無孔又粗， 五官又肉酸，鼻哥窿又大， 雙眼有無神， 牙齒唔整齊又黃<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔食了"},{"pid":"29f3d7d0926b025923bfc970e8bdbfab4aee6e93","tid":2179813,"uid":42734,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />褲都分享一個 褲鍾意食豬大腸 但豬大腸太肥 試過每一舊都咬完lur返出來"},{"pid":"4db209c693b219e149aaaf3e0b951b684519d442","tid":2179813,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29f3d7d0926b025923bfc970e8bdbfab4aee6e93","tid":2179813,"uid":42734,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />褲都分享一個 褲鍾意食豬大腸 但豬大腸太肥 試過每一舊都咬完lur返出來"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:44:45.000Z","msg":"你都吸晒啲精華同肥油了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次試下lur入面啲油<br />\n或者剪開佢剪走啲油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082a6f361283acd5334d